OL,3,CBonnie Tyler out of coma but recovery
OL,4,Cgoing to 'take time'
OL,6,FSinger Bonnie Tyler is no longer in a
OL,7,Fcoma but remains in intensive care and
OL,8,Fis "very unwell".
OL,10,FThe Welsh star had been placed in the
OL,11,Finduced coma to aid in her recovery
OL,12,Ffrom emergency intestinal surgery in
OL,13,FMay.
OL,15,FShe was admitted to a hospital near
OL,16,Fher home in Faro, Portugal.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
