OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781552859
OL,3,CBonnie Tyler out of coma but recovery
OL,4,Cgoing to 'take time'
OL,6,FOn Monday (June 15), an update on the
OL,7,Fsinger's official website said that
OL,8,Fdoctors are "confident" she will make
OL,9,Fa "good" recovery but warned that it
OL,10,Fwill "take time".
OL,12,FThe message from her team and family
OL,13,Falso confirmed that all remaining
OL,14,Fshows until the end of August will be
OL,15,Fcancelled or postponed until next
OL,16,Fyear, but they are "hopeful that our
OL,17,Fshows in the autumn will go ahead".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
