OL,3,CBonnie Tyler out of coma but recovery
OL,4,Cgoing to 'take time'
OL,6,FThe statement concluded: "We apologise
OL,7,Fto all of Bonnie's fans and to our
OL,8,Fpromoter partners for the
OL,9,Fdisappointment that this will cause
OL,10,Fbut trust that you will understand and
OL,11,Fbear with us in these difficult
OL,12,Fcircumstances. We hope to see you next
OL,13,Fyear instead.
OL,15,F"We would like to thank everyone for
OL,16,Fthe huge outpouring of love and
OL,17,Fsupport from all over the world that
OL,18,Fwe have received for Bonnie and want
OL,19,Fto tell you that she is aware of, and
OL,20,Fvery grateful for, your good wishes.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
